product.name: BOYFRIEND ORGANIC CREW T-SHIRT
product.description: The Boyfriend Organic Crew T-Shirt is made with 100% organic cotton fabric It features a crew neckline, short sleeves, and a relaxed fit Wear it casually with denim and sneakers Our model wears size AU Extra Small She usually wears a standard AU 8/Extra Small, is 180cm tall, and has a 78cm bust, 94cm hips and 62cm waist Relaxed fit Crew neckline Short sleeves Semi lightweight Non-sheer Some stretch 100% Organic Cotton Cold Hand Wash

product.name: VINTAGE DENIM JACKET
product.description: Our Vintage Denim Jacket is an easy-to-style must have for your wardrobe Made from a cotton blend denim, it features classic stitched seams, front and chest pockets and brushed silver-toned buttons Wear with a tee and your favourite pant or skirt Our model wears size AU 8/XS She usually wears a standard AU 8/Extra Small, is 180cm tall, and has a 78cm bust, 94cm hips and 62cm waist Relaxed fit Denim fabric Collar Chest pockets Silver-toned buttons Classic stitched seams Medium weight Light wash colourway 99% Cotton, 1% Elastine Wash and dry separately

product.name: CASUAL PANT
product.description: Built for comfort and style, the Casual Pant is made with cotton stretch fabric They feature an elasticated waist, front pockets, and front drawstring fastening Wear the Casual Pant with a white tee and sneakers for a great off-duty outfit Our model wears size AU 8 She usually wears a standard AU 8/Extra Small, is 177cm tall, and has an 85cm bust, 90cm hips and 62cm waist Front drawstring fastening Elasticated waist Front pockets Coin pocket on right hand side Back pockets Relaxed fit but slim towards the ankles Stretch fabric 95% Cotton, 5% Elastane Cold Hand Wash

product.name: LOLA LONGLINE RAINCOAT
product.description: The Lola Longline Raincoat is a must-have for your wardrobe It offers a relaxed fit, hood and a button-down front Wear it on cooler days with denim and sneakers Our model wears size AU 8/XS She usually wears a standard AU 8/Extra Small, is 180cm tall, and has a 78cm bust, 94cm hips and 62cm waist Relaxed fit Berry or navy blue colourways Two front pockets Hood Press stud buttons Water resistant Main: 50% Polyurethane, 50% Polyester/Lining: 100% Polyester Wipe with damp cloth

product.name: CLASSIC LEATHER SNEAKER
product.description: Don't go past our Classic Leather Sneaker Available in a timeless white colourway, they feature lace tie ups and a rounded toe Wear them casually with your favourite bottoms White colourway Lace tie up Rounded toe Timeless design Leather upper, canvas lining, rubber outsole Wipe with damp cloth
